    { id:"s3-transfer-accel-vs-dx-vs-vpn-vs-snow", label:"S3 Transfer Acceleration vs Direct Connect vs VPN vs Snowball vs Snowmobile", desc:"Ordered roughly by data volume and connectivity needs — from accelerated internet uploads to dedicated lines to physical devices for offline transfer." },
