    { id:"vpc-interface-vs-gateway-endpoint", label:"VPC Interface Endpoint vs Gateway Endpoint", desc:"Interface endpoints (via PrivateLink/ENI) support most AWS services and cost per hour; Gateway endpoints support only S3 and DynamoDB and are free." },
